<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><p>This function compares the model before and after design changes and displays the changes in a list or temporary graphic.</p><p><br></p><h2 class="fr-text-bordered">Features</h2><h3>Model comparison SP</h3><hr><p>Two CAD data can be compared side by side on the screen.</p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/D38E2639-DD4B-88D2-7999-135302BB3407.jpeg" alt="" class="fr-fic fr-dii"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/916B6265-B7E3-4E68-4252-0CD4EBBCA891.png" class="fr-fic fr-dib"><br></p><h3 align="center"><br></h3><h3>Extract shape difference SP</h3><hr><p>Two CAD data can be compared by overlapping them.<br><br><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/E7079A29-128A-37E9-8095-82FD611E7C39.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p align="center"><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/BD61F4D5-2669-7E71-E2B2-210FCF54AFFB.jpeg" alt="" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3><br></h3><h3 class="fr-text-bordered">Inquiries</h3><p>If you have any inquiries about our product or would like to request a visit to your place for explanation or demonstration, please use the inquiry form.</p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/contact"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Contact Us &rarr;</span></a></p></div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font